---
// Public interest form shown on /login while signup is gated. Posts to
// Formspree, redirects back to /login?registered=1 on success.
---

<section class="max-w-md mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="text-center mb-10">
    <p class="label-eyebrow mb-3">Åpner snart</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-3">Strikketorget</h1>
    <p class="text-charcoal/65">
      Vi pusser på siste finish før vi slipper Strikketorget for alle.
      Legg igjen e-posten din, så sier vi fra så snart du kan registrere
      deg.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-sage-500/10">
    <form
      action="https://formspree.io/f/mjgepbnq"
      method="POST"
      class="space-y-4"
    >
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="strikketorget" />
      <input type="hidden" name="source" value="login-gate" />
      <input
        type="hidden"
        name="_next"
        value={`${Astro.url.origin}/login?registered=1`}
      />

      <div>
        <label for="interest-email" class="label-form">E-post</label>
        <input
          id="interest-email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          required
          autocomplete="email"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-sage-500/20 bg-linen/50 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-terracotta-500"
          placeholder="navn@eksempel.no"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="interest-name" class="label-form">Navn (valgfritt)</label>
        <input
          id="interest-name"
          name="name"
          type="text"
          autocomplete="name"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-sage-500/20 bg-linen/50 px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-terracotta-500"
        />
      </div>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="btn-primary w-full rounded-full py-3 px-5 text-sm font-semibold"
      >
        Meld interesse
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <p class="text-center text-xs text-charcoal/40 mt-6">
    Vi sender bare én e-post når vi åpner. Ingen reklame, ingen spam.
  </p>
</section>
